<p><span class="anchor" id="p45"></span>وَفِي الْقَدِيم تَتَرَبَّص تِسْعَة أشهر<a href="#p45" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p46"></span>مُدَّة الْحمل غَالِبا<a href="#p46" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
